OSX Terminal.app
----------------

* View -> Show tab bar
* Preferences -> Settings -> Copy Homebrew to Kimo
  * Make default
  * Uncheck "Blink cursor"
  * Font: Monaco Regular 11pt.
  * Antialias text
  * Keyboard -> "Use option as meta key"
  * Advanced -> Uncheck "Audible bell"
  * Window -> Background -> Opacity: 100%
  * Shell -> When the shell exits: Close the window
* Preferences -> startup
  * New tables open with: Default working Directory
